# No environment variables are required for the MVP.
#
# Sessions use random tokens stored hashed in D1, so there is no signing secret.
# If you add secrets later (e.g. API keys for WhatsApp/SMS notifications):
#   - local dev:   put them in a `.dev.vars` file (gitignored), e.g. MY_SECRET=value
#   - production:  npx wrangler secret put MY_SECRET
